creator_credit: Tamasin Simpkin, Guesswork Television and Katering Productions
brief_description: Having conquered the cutthroat world of satirical online cooking shows with The Katering Show, the two Kates are ready to take a Sassy Swipe at morning lifestyle television in Get Krack!n.

constellations_other.description: Two of the most striking costumes on the big and small screens embody the glamour of leading First Peoples ladies.
